# =============================================================================
# FLASHBOTS PRIVATE EXECUTION - For bypassing mempool latency
# =============================================================================
# Flashbots allows private bundle submission - your transactions won't be visible
# to public mempool bots, eliminating frontrunning risk.
#
# Get started:
# 1. Get an Alchemy API key (free): https://dashboard.alchemy.com/
# 2. Set your wallet private key (DO NOT share!)
# 3. Add funds to your wallet for gas
#
# Configuration:
# ETH_RPC_URL=https://eth-mainnet.g.alchemy.com/v2/YOUR_ALCHEMY_KEY
# BOT_WALLET_PRIVATE_KEY=0xyour_private_key_here
#
# Optional: Flashbots-specific settings
# FLASHBOTS_PRIORITY_FEE=0.01 (ETH - for validator tip)
# FLASHBOTS_MAX_BASE_FEE=0.1 (ETH - max base fee to accept)
